{"tid":2224252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"默克爾：「一國兩制」屢遭削弱　今後需向北京表達擔憂","createTime":"2020-09-30T11:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T13:12:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c9a3364777435094f242f79cb91cc0630f65a5","tid":2224252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552475-20200930.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552475-20200930.htm&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=da5cff31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552475-20200930.htm&h=6250ab1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552475-20200930.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾指責中國惡劣與殘酷對待中國少數民族，並對北京打壓香港異見人士表達深切關注。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾在歐盟領導人峰會舉行前夕，到德國聯邦議會發表講話，認為「一國兩制」原則一次又一次遭到削弱，強調今後與北京的所有對話中，都必須提出人權問題，以及對香港局勢的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾又說，歐盟與中國在商討投資協定方面，目前未有太大進展，重申歐盟希望與中國進行公平貿易，希望雙方到年底前，在互惠互利、市場准入方面取得突破。"},{"pid":"32cbafda7551777f3769da82020058d3df54c66b","tid":2224252,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4f298d3cdc0590ccd3ce5a212745a03b6c4b3","tid":2224252,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"我一直在關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93619969655edf25eaf3bf6d05f030cfea672b08","tid":2224252,"uid":143230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"好擔憂<br />\n但係都要繼續奶"},{"pid":"f49935350835f71fc5e1eba9a6d08a8ea7432884","tid":2224252,"uid":200280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;歐盟與中國在商討投資協